content.text: Now let me check the actual data - the current male-to-female ratio among those with abnormal uric acid:

input.command:
sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/thrombosis_prediction.sqlite" "
SELECT 
  SUM(CASE WHEN P.SEX = 'M' AND L.UA <= 8.0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS abnormal_males,
  SUM(CASE WHEN P.SEX = 'F' AND L.UA <= 6.5 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS abnormal_females,
  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN P.SEX = 'M' AND L.UA <= 8.0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) / 
  SUM(CASE WHEN P.SEX = 'F' AND L.UA <= 6.5 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ratio
FROM Laboratory L
JOIN Patient P ON L.ID = P.ID
WHERE L.UA IS NOT NULL;
"
